title: Cartoonist-in-Residence to give first public meeting (University of Windsor)
text: ( Source : University of Windsor ) Scott Chantler, the English Department 's first Cartoonist-in-Residence, will give an inaugural reading Tuesday, October 6, from 4 p.m. to 6 p.m. at Cantebury College . Chantler, who took his post in September,
